channel.title: Comments on: OCC Lip Tar Pretty Boy

item.title: By: Erin-Kurley
item.dc:creator: Erin-Kurley
item.description: I feel like I finally found the lip product of my dreams! Color that actually lasts and wears beautifully under chap stick. I swear my lips were still a little pink this morning!
item.content:encoded: I feel like I finally found the lip product of my dreams! Color that actually lasts and wears beautifully under chap stick. I swear my lips were still a little pink this morning!

item.title: By: Sarah Cosper
item.dc:creator: Sarah Cosper
item.description:
In reply to <a href="/occ-lip-tar-pretty-boy/#comment-169">JCPC</a>.
It pretty much just dries to whatever your lips are without any product. I put a little lip balm over the top for comfort.
